    "description": "NoBroker Global Group, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Software Engineer for our Dhanbad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout NoBroker Global Group:\nNoBroker Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with NoBroker Global Group!",
